cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper presents an end-to-end deep learning approach for Compressed Learning (CL) for image classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the paper deals with image classification. The paper also involves linear projections of signals, which falls under the category of cs.IT (Information Theory). The use of neural networks for non-linear inference suggests the category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
